---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Help | FashionCulture">
    <main>
        <section class="help-section">
            <h1>How Can We Help You?</h1>

            <div class="content-block">
                <p>
                    At FashionCulture, we are dedicated to providing you with the best shopping experience possible. If you have any questions or need assistance, we're here to help. Below you'll find answers to common questions and ways to get in touch with us.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>How do I place an order?</strong>
                        <p>Placing an order is easy! Simply browse our collection, select your desired items, and add them to your cart. When you're ready, proceed to checkout and follow the prompts to complete your purchase.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>What payment methods do you accept?</strong>
                        <p>We accept various payment methods, including credit/debit cards, PayPal, and other secure payment gateways. You can view all available payment options at checkout.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>How can I track my order?</strong>
                        <p>Once your order has been shipped, you'll receive a confirmation email with a tracking number. You can use this number to track your order on the carrier's website.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>What is your return policy?</strong>
                        <p>We want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase. If you need to return an item, please visit our <a href="/return-policy">Return Policy</a> page for detailed instructions.</p>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>How do I contact customer support?</strong>
                        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please reach out to our customer support team at <a href="mailto:support@fashionculture.com">support@fashionculture.com</a>. We're here to help!</p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you couldn't find the answer to your question in our FAQs, don't hesitate to contact us. Our customer support team is available to assist you with any inquiries or issues you may have.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@fashionculture.com">support@fashionculture.com</a></li>
                    <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +1-800-123-4567</li>
                    <li><strong>Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM (EST)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Shipping and Delivery</h2>
                <p>For more information on shipping methods, costs, and delivery times, please visit our <a href="/delivery-information">Delivery Information</a> page.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Returns and Exchanges</h2>
                <p>Need to return or exchange an item? Please review our <a href="/return-policy">Return Policy</a> for details on how to initiate a return or exchange.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p>Your privacy is important to us. To learn more about how we handle your personal information, please read our <a href="/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <style>
        main {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .help-section {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #444;
        }

        h2 {
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #555;
        }

        p, li {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .content-block {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        strong {
            color: #000;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</Layout>
